            "entries": [
                {
                    "type": "item",
                    "name": "minecraft:enchanted_book",
                    "functions": [
                        {
                            "function": "minecraft:set_nbt",
                            "tag": "{id:\"dawn:dawn_disillusionment\",display:{Name:'{\"text\":\"[记忆碎片] 黎明·幻灭\",\"italic\":false,\"color\":\"yellow\"}'}}"
                        },
                        {
                            "function": "set_lore",
                            "lore": [
                                {
                                    "text": "",
                                    "bold": false,
                                    "italic": true,
                                    "underlined": false,
                                    "strikethrough": false,
                                    "obfuscated": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "她是个善良的人，一直如此。尽管自己的人生已经陷入绝境，",
                                    "bold": false,
                                    "italic": true,
                                    "underlined": false,
                                    "strikethrough": false,
                                    "obfuscated": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "她仍旧愿意尽己所能的去帮助他人。她的友善为她带来了许多",
                                    "bold": false,
                                    "italic": true,
                                    "underlined": false,
                                    "strikethrough": false,
                                    "obfuscated": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "朋友，她甚至因此再一次感受到了幸福。但人类的生命太过短",
                                    "bold": false,
                                    "italic": true,
                                    "underlined": false,
                                    "strikethrough": false,
                                    "obfuscated": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "暂，随着时间流逝，她的朋友一个个离她而去。而随着每个人",
                                    "bold": false,
                                    "italic": true,
                                    "underlined": false,
                                    "strikethrough": false,
                                    "obfuscated": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "的逝去，她所倾注的感情也一并消失了。在痛苦之中她的性格",
                                    "bold": false,
                                    "italic": true,
                                    "underlined": false,
                                    "strikethrough": false,
                                    "obfuscated": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "发生了翻天覆地的改变，她不愿再让任何人在自己的心中留下",
                                    "bold": false,
                                    "italic": true,
                                    "underlined": false,
                                    "strikethrough": false,
                                    "obfuscated": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "印记。她变得庄严，冷漠，令人畏惧，却只是因为害怕离别时",
                                    "bold": false,
                                    "italic": true,
                                    "underlined": false,
                                    "strikethrough": false,
                                    "obfuscated": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "的痛苦。",
                                    "bold": false,
                                    "italic": true,
                                    "underlined": false,
                                    "strikethrough": false,
                                    "obfuscated": false
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}